
Project_Page_UI.fig
AECS — AvizSazeh Engineering UX System

NOTE: Structured Figma specification (non-binary format)

=========================================================
1. PAGE STRUCTURE
=========================================================

[1] PROJECT HERO SECTION
- Title: Engineering Case Studies
- Subtitle: From architectural problem → system execution
- Visual: industrial documentation background
- CTA: View Engineering Breakdown

[2] PROJECT FILTER SYSTEM
- system type filter
- complexity filter
- industry filter

[3] CASE STUDY GRID
- 3 column layout
- each card shows:
  - problem summary
  - system type
  - execution preview

[4] FEATURED PROJECT DEEP DIVE
- Problem Definition
- Engineering Challenge
- System Design
- Manufacturing Process
- Execution Process
- Final Result

[5] ENGINEERING BREAKDOWN LAYER
- structural logic
- material system
- installation constraints

[6] EXECUTION DOCUMENTATION
- site photos
- control checkpoints
- QA/QC notes

[7] PROJECT CTA ENGINE
- "Request Similar Engineering System"

=========================================================
2. UI RULES
=========================================================

- 12 column grid system
- 8px spacing system
- documentary engineering style
- no marketing language
- emphasis on proof over presentation

=========================================================
3. COMPONENTS
=========================================================

ProjectHero
ProjectFilterSystem
CaseStudyGrid
CaseStudyCard
ProjectDeepDive
EngineeringBreakdown
ExecutionDocumentation
ProjectCTA

